HelpTooltip:
Calculates the difference between the first input and
the second input and outputs this value.

First Input port and Second Input port connect to a
Feature Extractor or a Datatype node. Both inputs
must be of the same type. Live Data Out port
connects to a DataType, Velocity, Record Examples
and Machine Learning System nodes.
PortTooltip: Connect a Feature Extract or Data Type node
Coonect to Data In port. Outputs a float value.

tips: Float value of distance between inputs
